<div id="review_3813459987" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3813459987" />
    <a title="Linda" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/9773635-linda"><img alt="Linda" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1337961417p2/9773635.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3813459987?book_show_action=true">Feb 19, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Linda" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Linda" href="/user/show/9773635-linda">Linda</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3813459987" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17796156451624073270">As always, John Irving takes the reader on an intense and varied journey through varied cultures and mysteries. I love his insights and parallel plots all going on at the same time; no time to be bored or distracted.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


